 RadioButtonList
 A radio button list lets merchants select from a given set of options.
 Props
 Name Type Description
 items string[] The radio button options.
 onItemSelected (item: string) => void A callback to be performed when the radio list item is selected.
 initialSelectedItem string? The name of the selected item when the radio button list is first rendered.
 initialOffsetToShowSelectedItem boolean? Whether the initialSelectedItem renders at the top of the list.
